    {
      "title": "[正面] This is a really good game surprisingly at least f...",
      "summary": "This is a really good game surprisingly at least for me since I am not much a fan of Card games but this one has been enjoyable this far.\n\nI really like the Lovercraftian art direction and inspiration since I am a sucker for lovecraftian stuff.\n\nThe only thing I may have to point out is that progression can be a bit slow in terms of leveling up my characters I don't like having to wait days to get them at a agood enough level,given it may be partially my fault as I try to focus on two teams instead of one to stay versataile.\n\nThe Story may not be a Masterpiece but its actually good at least where I am right now at least which is not something natural in a Gacha game but I am interested in the story..tried switching the languages from English to German which is not that great its servicable but English overall has a bit of a higher translation quality compared to the German one in this game and its all AI translated in which I don't personally take any issues with I rather have this than any activist translators abusing their position to insert political nonsense into the game and the translation is alright for now.",
